---
description: NativeWind
globs: 
alwaysApply: false
---
- Use className prop instead of StyleSheet for all styling (e.g., className="bg-blue-500 p-4")
- Create consistent spacing with p-[number] and m-[number] classes
- Implement responsive layouts with flex, justify, and items classes
- Use dark: prefix for dark mode styling (e.g., className="bg-white dark:bg-black")
- Group related styles into reusable className strings for consistency
- Add tw-prefixed comments above complex className strings to explain intent
- Use dynamic classes with template literals for conditional styling
- Extend tailwind.config.js for custom colors, spacing, or components
- Avoid inline styles when NativeWind classes would work
